// DJDoyle1's antiLag
import java.io.*;

public class antilag
{

public int ResetTimer = 0;

public void resetserver()
{
misc.println("Kicking Nulls...");
PlayerHandler.kickNick = null;
PlayerHandler.kickNick = "";
misc.println("Nulls Kicked");
PlayerHandler.kickAllPlayers = true;
misc.println("Saving game for all players");
ResetTimer = 0;
}
public void process()
{
ResetTimer += 1;
if(ResetTimer >= 600)
{
resetserver();
}
}
}
